      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "林彪上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00002",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "引子",
      "speakers": [
        "林彪"
      ],
      "text": "官居一品在朝堂，赤心耿耿报君王。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00003",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "林彪"
      ],
      "text": "幞头象简紫罗纱，执掌朝纲宰相家。枣红织就红罗缎，十字锦上绣团花。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00004",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林彪"
      ],
      "text": "下官林彪，我在妙庄王驾下称臣。我主得了思儿之病，宣召医官治疗。医官言道：若得圣驾病体痊愈，必得上香山，取三皇姑手眼。圣旨到来，命我林彪，去到香山。王命在身，怎敢不往。",
      "text_length": 83
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00005",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮慢板",
      "speakers": [
        "林彪"
      ],
      "text": "我主得病在金銮，忙坏了满朝文武并两班。请来医官调治把病探，言到此去非等闲：若得圣驾病体好，还得上香山去取手眼。我在此处莫久站，一到香山取手眼。",
      "text_length": 71
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00006",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "林彪下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00007",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "妙善上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00008",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮慢板",
      "speakers": [
        "妙善"
      ],
      "text": "一朝天子身有恙，想儿得病不下床。香山寺里闲游逛，四大天王摆两旁：这一个手执黄罗伞，那一个怀抱琵琶响叮当；这一个手执斩妖剑，那一个花皮貂在手内藏。他本是纣朝手内四员将，死后封神万古扬。妙善女到就观音相，等一等就要取药方。",
      "text_length": 109
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00009",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "林彪上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00010",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "林彪"
      ],
      "text": "圣上金殿把旨传，命我林彪到香山。双膝忙跪香山寺，要取手眼转回还。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00011",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "妙善"
      ],
      "text": "下跪者可是林彪么？",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00012",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林彪"
      ],
      "text": "是臣。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00013",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "妙善"
      ],
      "text": "为何不抬头？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00014",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林彪"
      ],
      "text": "小臣不敢。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00015",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "妙善"
      ],
      "text": "抬起头来。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00016",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林彪"
      ],
      "text": "尊菩萨敕命。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00017",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "妙善"
      ],
      "text": "老林彪是忠臣不必害怕，一件件一桩桩细说根芽：大公主、二公主俱招驸马，撇下了三孩儿情愿出家。血淋淋拿宝剑将眼挖下，无奈何举宝剑将手落下。老林彪在此处没要久站，回朝去见你主细说根芽。",
      "text_length": 89
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00018",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "林彪"
      ],
      "text": "香山寺里把头叩，回朝去见我主细说根由。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00019",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "妙善"
      ],
      "text": "唗！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00020",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "妙善"
      ],
      "text": "好一个忠臣老林彪，为父王前来把香烧。若得圣驾病体好，准备君妃把香烧。",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00021",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "林彪、妙善同下。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00022",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "太监、妙庄王同上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00023",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "引子",
      "speakers": [
        "妙庄王"
      ],
      "text": "患病在金銮，去取手连眼。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00024",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "妙庄王"
      ],
      "text": "朕，妙庄王在位。今天得了思儿想女之病，命林彪去取手眼，不见到来。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00025",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "林彪上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00026",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林彪"
      ],
      "text": "走哇！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00027",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "林彪"
      ],
      "text": "头顶香盘上金銮，启奏我主圣驾前。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00028",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林彪"
      ],
      "text": "这是臣取来手眼。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00029",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "妙庄王看。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00030",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "哭",
      "speakers": [
        "妙庄王"
      ],
      "text": "儿啦，儿啦儿啦！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00031",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林彪"
      ],
      "text": "臣还有本奏。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00032",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "妙庄王"
      ],
      "text": "有何本奏？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00033",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "林彪"
      ],
      "text": "若得圣驾病体痊愈，还得我主上山亲还愿。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00034",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "妙庄王"
      ],
      "text": "也罢。内臣！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00035",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "太监"
      ],
      "text": "有。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00036",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "妙庄王"
      ],
      "text": "将手眼挂在御书架上，看车辇。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00037",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王后上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00038",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "妙庄王"
      ],
      "text": "可惜为王做事错，不该举火烧殿阁。仰头进了天王殿，四大天王长得恶。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00039",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "王后"
      ],
      "text": "这一个手执浑元伞，",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00040",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "妙庄王"
      ],
      "text": "那一个怀抱琵琶唱清歌。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00041",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "王后"
      ],
      "text": "这一个手执斩妖剑，",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00042",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "妙庄王"
      ],
      "text": "那一个手执降妖磨。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00043",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "王后"
      ],
      "text": "他本是纣朝手里四员将，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00044",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮散板",
      "speakers": [
        "妙庄王"
      ],
      "text": "死后封神也不错。双膝跪在大佛殿，我封你全手全眼佛。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00045",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮二六板",
      "speakers": [
        "妙善"
      ],
      "text": "妙善女站云头一声高叫，老父王、龙国太细听根苗：儿非是孽灵魂邪魔外崇，儿是个拦路鬼把路来调。儿是你三孩儿公主妙善，咱父女相见在今朝。举家人卧龙殿劝儿开荤，那一时三孩儿烈性不从。我父王端来的唐鸭美酒，又端来荤馒头劝儿开荤。那一时我不从父王大命，将孩儿打在绞连皇宫。腊月里儿哭的百花开放，叫城隍真儿助宫绞连宫。儿哭的天昏地又暗，那一时三孩儿无有救星。有大鸟在空中苦苦相救，一阵风将孩儿刮过黄河以东。刮到了白衣庵修真养性，洗了手净了面才把香焚。咱朝里奸佞臣奏了一本，他言到白衣庵男女不分。恼坏了花花精三百僧众，可怜那五百姑一命归阴。劝父王把江山不坐也稳，倒不如同儿去上山修真。",
      "text_length": 284
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00046",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "妙庄王"
      ],
      "text": "君也错来臣也错，三皇姑出家成了佛。十万里江山让臣不坐，香山寺里去修佛。",
      "text_length": 35
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00047",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "王后"
      ],
      "text": "君也错，臣也错，三皇姑出家成了佛。十万里江山让臣臣不坐，香山寺里念弥陀。",
      "text_length": 36
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00048",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "妙善"
      ],
      "text": "三十三天天外天，卧龙殿上改茅山。有心与父再讲话，一阵香烟上西天。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00049",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "妙善下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00050",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "妙庄王",
        "王后",
        "林彪"
      ],
      "text": "阿弥陀佛！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01016018_e00051",
      "play_id": "01016018",
      "scene_id": "01016018_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众人同下。",
      "text_length": 5
    }
  ],
  "roles_inferred": true
}